<br>
I have just started doing the Spirocs tonight, and a pull of 4 watchers gets me ~8% xp at 44, not too shabby. I'm told this is good till aroud 48, at which point i'll move on to CS. Wyverns and Spirocs can be heavily contended for, depends if you can play off hours or not or your server.<br>
